.4</span> 标题：库房、银库、宝库（treasury, strongroom）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אֲרוֹן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’aron)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:10\">2KI 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:11\">2KI 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:8\">2CH 24:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:10\">2CH 24:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:11\">2CH 24:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:11\">2CH 24:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בַּיִת, אָסֹף</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：(beyth) ’asupim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:15\">1CH 26:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:17\">1CH 26:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בַּיִת, אוֹצָר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：(beyth) ’otsar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:12\">DEU 28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:34\">DEU 32:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:19\">JOS 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:24\">JOS 6:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:51\">1KI 7:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18\">1KI 15:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18\">1KI 15:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:19\">2KI 12:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:14\">2KI 14:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:8\">2KI 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:15\">2KI 18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:15\">2KI 20:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:13\">2KI 24:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:13\">2KI 24:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:26\">1CH 9:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:20\">1CH 26:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:20\">1CH 26:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:22\">1CH 26:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:24\">1CH 26:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:26\">1CH 26:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:25\">1CH 27:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:25\">1CH 27:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:12\">1CH 28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:12\">1CH 28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:8\">1CH 29:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:1\">2CH 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:15\">2CH 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:9\">2CH 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:9\">2CH 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:2\">2CH 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:24\">2CH 25:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27\">2CH 32:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:69\">EZR 2:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:69\">NEH 7:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:70\">NEH 7:70</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:39\">NEH 10:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:21\">PRO 8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:4\">EZK 28:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:2\">DAN 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:15\">HOS 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">MAL 3:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בַּיִת, נְכֹאת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：beth nkoth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:2\">ISA 39:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">兰：גְּנַז</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：gnaz)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:20\">EZR 7:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：גֶּנֶז</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：genez)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:9\">EST 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:7\">EST 4:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：גַּנְזַךְ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：ganzak)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:11\">1CH 28:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：γαζοφυλάκιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：gazofulakion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41\">MRK 12:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:41\">MRK 12:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:43\">MRK 12:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1\">LUK 21:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:20\">JHN 8:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc3:28\">1MA 3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc14:49\">1MA 14:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:6\">2MA 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:24\">2MA 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:28\">2MA 3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:40\">2MA 3:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc4:42\">2MA 4:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc5:18\">2MA 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc4:3\">4MA 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc4:6\">4MA 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd5:44\">1ES 5:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd8:18\">1ES 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd8:44\">1ES 8:44</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：θησαυρός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：thēsauros)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir1:25\">SIR 1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc3:29\">1MA 3:29</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κορβανᾶς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：korbanas)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:6\">MAT 27:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ταμιεῖον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tamieion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir29:12\">SIR 29:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：θησαυρός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：thesaurus)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc4:7\">4MA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd6:40\">2ES 6:40</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/PTZ-0075_pinnacle_hans.jpg\" alt=\"圣殿山的西南角\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">圣殿山的西南角 (© Ray Pritz by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>宝库是用来存放君王或其他国家行政机构的贵重物品的地方。耶路撒冷圣殿有自己的库房。库房没有标准的大小或结构。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:10\">2KI 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:11\">2KI 12:11</a> 和（《和》12:9–10）<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:8\">2CH 24:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:10\">2CH 24:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:11\">2CH 24:11</a> 中，希伯来文<em>’aron</em> 指的是一个很大的奉献箱。根据<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:10\">2KI 12:10</a> （《和》12:9），这种箱子的“门”上开有一个洞。“门”指的是箱子的一个表面，可能是箱子的顶面。以色列人可以把他们的捐项（不是硬币，因为当时还没有发明出来），通过这个洞塞到箱子里面。之后，打开或取下箱子的顶，就可以取出捐项。</p>\n<p>在一些经文中，希伯来文<em>’otsar</em> 指的是宝物（treasure；如<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:13\">2KI 24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:9\">2CH 12:9</a> ）；而在另一些经文中，这个词指的是储存宝物的地方，即库房（treasury；如<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27\">2CH 32:27</a> ）。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:18\">1KI 15:18</a> 前半节的原文字面意思是：“亚撒取了耶和华殿的 库房里剩下的所有金银，（他又取了）王宫中的宝物”。我们所查阅的译本都没有区分这两层意思，有些译本把两个词都译为“宝物”（“treasures”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ），还有译本把它们都译为“库房”（“treasuries”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> ）。事实上，在提到<em>’otsar</em> 的许多经文中，很难确定它的意思是“宝物”还是“库房”。在希伯来文中，只有三处经文明确提到“宝物间”（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:39\">NEH 10:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:2\">DAN 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">MAL 3:10</a> ）。</p>\n<p>如果目标语言没有表示“库房”的词语，则可以使用描述性短语，例如，“存放／看守王（或圣殿）的贵重物品的地方）”。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:6\">MAT 27:6</a> 的后半节也可以译成：“把它和圣殿的钱放在一起是违犯律法的，因为这是血钱。”</p>\n<p>在新约中，希腊文<em>gazofulakion</em> 也指一种用来收奉献的箱子。根据犹太传统，圣殿中有13个这样的奉献箱，让金钱滑到箱子里面的开口是号角形或羊角形的。因此，钱币掉进箱子里的声音非常响亮。在有些文化中，人们并不知道这种奉献箱，或者最多只知道教堂里传来传去收取奉献的袋子。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:1\">LUK 21:1</a> 中，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 将这个词译为“Temple money box”（“圣殿钱箱”），并加上了以下附注：“犹太人敬拜场所内一种特殊的盒子，人们把他们献给上帝的礼物放到里面。”PV 使用了一个较长的译法，意为：“专门装它们（礼物）的地方。”</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
